## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- [Guild CLI](https://github.com/guild-framework/guild-core) installed
- API keys configured for your chosen providers:
{{- range $provider, $config := .vars.providers }}
  - {{ $provider | title }}: Set `{{ $config.api_key_env | default (printf "%s_API_KEY" ($provider | upper)) }}` environment variable
{{- end }}

### Initialize the Campaign

1. **Start the daemon** (if auto-start is disabled):
   ```bash
   guild daemon start
   ```

2. **Verify guild configuration**:
   ```bash
   guild status
   ```

3. **Create your first commission**:
   ```bash
   guild commission create --interactive
   ```

4. **Start working with your guild**:
   ```bash
   guild chat
   ```

